<TD>

Add.<BR>
<BR><BR>Algorithm:<BR><BR>
<FONT FACE="Courier">
operand1 = operand1 + operand2
</FONT>
<BR><BR>Example:<PRE><FONT FACE="Courier">MOV AL, 5   ; AL = 5
ADD AL, -3  ; AL = 2
RET</FONT></PRE>

